## Create answer


### Resource

`<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>/v1/questions/:question_id/answers`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------
question_id | Question ID | yes


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`POST`


### HTTP headers

<%= partial 'includes/http/headers/auth' %>


### HTTP body

{
	"answer": {
		"type": "Question::Single",
		"body": {
			"yes": "Yes",
			"no": "No"
		}
	}
}


### Note
Required keys:
* `type`;
* `body`.

`type` key has to contains one of the following values:
* `Answer::AnalogueScale`;
* `Answer::BarGraph`;
* `Answer::Feedback`;
* `Answer::FollowUpContact`;
* `Answer::Grid`;
* `Answer::Information`;
* `Answer::Multiple`;
* `Answer::Number`;
* `Answer::Single`;
* `Answer::TextBox`;
* `Answer::Url`.


> HTTP example request

```http
POST <%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>/v1/questions/1/answers
```

```http
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
access-token: xxxyyyzzz
token-type: Bearer
client: xxxyyyzzz
uid: user@<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>
```

```json
{
	"answer": {
		"type": "Question::Single",
		"body": {
			"yes": "Yes",
			"no": "No"
		}
	}
}
```


> HTTP response 200 OK
